node.title: Section of SH1 closed after serious crash in Waikato
node.description: Emergency services are responding to a serious crash on State Highway 1 near Tirau.
node.content:
["Emergency services are responding to a serious crash on State Highway 1 near Tirau in Waikato.", "", "
Police say the crash near Momona Road in Piarere was reported about 8.30pm. Photo: RNZ / Patrice Allen
", "The police say the crash near Momona Road in Piarere was reported about 8.30pm and involves a single vehicle.", "A section of SH1 is closed and motorists are asked to divert onto SH29 and SH27 (from Tirau) to avoid the affected area."]
